90void
91convert_output(void)
92{
93 if (XBIT(49, 1))
94 return;
95
96 if (flg.opt >= 2 && !XBIT(47, 0x10)) {
97 init_collapse();
98 collapse_arrays();
99 }
100 convert_statements();
101 FREE(ftb.base);
102 comm_fini();
103 freearea(FORALL_AREA);
104 if (flg.opt >= 2 && !XBIT(47, 0x10)) {
105 collapse_allocates(TRUE);
106 end_collapse();
107 }
108 eliminate_barrier();
109 free_brtbl();
110 transform_wrapup();
111 convert_simple();
112 if (XBIT(58, 0x10000000))
113 convert_template_instance();
114}

116/*
117 * keep track of forall temp arrays
118 *
119 */
120#define TEMP_AREA 6
121
122typedef struct T_LIST {
123 struct T_LIST *next;
124 int temp, asd, dtype, cvlen, sc, std, astd, dstd;
125} T_LIST;
126
127#define GET_T_LIST(q) q = (T_LIST *)getitem(TEMP_AREA, sizeof(T_LIST))
128static T_LIST *templist;
129static int beforestd;
130static int newsymnum;

132static void
133early_flow_init(void)
134{
135 optshrd_init();
136 flowgraph();
137 findloop(0);
138 flow();
139}
140
141static void
142early_flow_fini(void)
143{
144 optshrd_fend();
145 optshrd_end();
146}
147
148void
149forall_dependency_analyze(void)
150{
151 int std;
152 int ast;
153 int parallel_depth;
154 int task_depth;
155
156 templist = NULL;
157 parallel_depth = 0;
158 task_depth = 0;
159 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std;) {
160 ast = STD_AST(std);
161 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
162 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
163 ++parallel_depth;
164 set_descriptor_sc(SC_PRIVATE);
165 break;
166 case A_MP_ENDPARALLEL:
167 --parallel_depth;
168 if (parallel_depth == 0 && task_depth == 0) {
169 set_descriptor_sc(SC_LOCAL);
170 }
171 break;
172 case A_MP_TASK:
173 case A_MP_TASKLOOP:
174 ++task_depth;
175 set_descriptor_sc(SC_PRIVATE);
176 break;
177 case A_MP_ENDTASK:
178 case A_MP_ETASKLOOP:
179 --task_depth;
180 if (parallel_depth == 0 && task_depth == 0) {
181 set_descriptor_sc(SC_LOCAL);
182 }
183 break;
184 case A_FORALL:
185 if (STD_DELETE(std)) {
186 ast_to_comment(ast);
187 std = STD_NEXT(std);
188 continue;
189 }
190 forall_dependency(std);
191 break;
192 }
193 std = STD_NEXT(std);
194 }
195 freearea(TEMP_AREA);
196 templist = NULL;
197}
198
199void
200convert_forall(void)
201{
202 int std;
203 int ast;
204
205 if (XBIT(49, 2))
206 return;
207
208 if (flg.opt >= 2 && XBIT(53, 2)) {
209 points_to();
210 }
211 /*
212 * need to do early flow analysis to determine if lhs really need temp.
213 * NOTE: -Hx,4,0x200000 is not useful at all; eventually a crash could
214 * occur in nmeutil because a NME table is not created (nmeb.stg_base is
215 * null).
216 */
217 if (flg.opt >= 2 && !XBIT(4, 0x200000)) {
218 early_flow_init();
219 }
220
221 if (!XBIT(4, 0x100000))
222 forall_dependency_analyze();
223 /* we need to redo the flow graph forall_dependency_analyze can add more node
224 * into the flow */
225 init_region();
226 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std;) {
227 arg_gbl.inforall = FALSE;
228 ast = STD_AST(std);
229 check_region(std);
230 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
231 case A_FORALL:
232 arg_gbl.inforall = TRUE;
233 std = conv_forall(std);
234 break;
235 default:
236 std = STD_NEXT(std);
237 break;
238 }
239 }
240 if (flg.smp) {
241 convert_omp_workshare();
242 }
243 if (flg.opt >= 2 && !XBIT(4, 0x200000)) {
244 early_flow_fini();
245 }
246 if (flg.opt >= 2 && XBIT(53, 2)) {
247 f90_fini_pointsto();
248 }
249}
250
251#define NO_WRKSHR 0
252#define IN_WRKSHR 1
253#define IN_PDO 2
254#define IN_SINGLE 3
255#define IN_PARALLEL 4
256#define IN_CRITICAL 5
257
258static int
259gen_pdo(int do_ast)
260{
261 int ast;
262
263 ast = mk_stmt(A_MP_PDO, 0);
264 A_DOVARP(ast, A_DOVARG(do_ast));
265 A_LASTVALP(ast, A_LASTVALG(do_ast));
266 A_M1P(ast, A_M1G(do_ast));
267 A_M2P(ast, A_M2G(do_ast));
268 A_M3P(ast, A_M3G(do_ast));
269 A_CHUNKP(ast, 0);
270 A_SCHED_TYPEP(ast, 0); /* STATIC */
271 A_ORDEREDP(ast, 0);
272 A_LASTVALP(ast, 0);
273 A_DISTRIBUTEP(ast, 0);
274 A_DISTPARDOP(ast, 0);
275 A_ENDLABP(ast, 0);
276 A_DISTCHUNKP(ast, 0);
277 A_TASKLOOPP(ast, 0);
278
279 return ast;
280}
281
282static void
283gen_endsingle(int std, int single, int presinglebarrier)
284{
285 int ompast;
286 int ompstd;
287 int singlestd = A_STDG(single);
288
289 if (presinglebarrier &&
290 A_TYPEG(STD_AST(STD_PREV(singlestd))) != A_MP_BARRIER) {
291 add_stmt_before(mk_stmt(A_MP_BARRIER, 0), singlestd);
292 }
293
294 ompast = mk_stmt(A_MP_ENDSINGLE, 0);
295 A_LOPP(single, ompast);
296 A_LOPP(ompast, single);
297 ompstd = add_stmt_before(ompast, std);
298 add_stmt_after(mk_stmt(A_MP_BARRIER, 0), ompstd);
299}
300
301static void
302convert_omp_workshare(void)
303{
304 int std;
305 int newstd = 0;
306 int ast;
307 int lsptr;
308 int prevast;
309 int state = NO_WRKSHR;
310 int dolevel = 0;
311 int parallellevel = 0;
312 int wherelevel = 0;
313 int ompast;
314 int ompstd;
315 int single;
316 int presinglebarrier = 0;
317 int parallel_depth = 0;
318
319 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = STD_NEXT(std)) {
320 ast = STD_AST(std);
321 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
322 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
323 ++parallel_depth;
324 break;
325 case A_MP_ENDPARALLEL:
326 --parallel_depth;
327 break;
328 case A_MP_WORKSHARE:
329 case A_MP_ENDWORKSHARE:
330 if (parallel_depth > 1) {
331 ast_to_comment(ast);
332 ast = STD_AST(std);
333 }
334 break;
335 }
336
337 if (state != NO_WRKSHR && A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ALLOC &&
338 A_TKNG(ast) == TK_DEALLOCATE) {
339 int sptr = sym_of_ast(A_SRCG(ast));
340 if (CCSYMG(sptr) || HCCSYMG(sptr)) {
341 /* dealloc of a compiler generated temp, make sure
342 * any OMP SINGLEs are preceded by a barrier */
343 presinglebarrier++;
344 }
345 }
346
347 switch (state) {
348 case NO_WRKSHR:
349 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_MP_WORKSHARE) {
350 state = IN_WRKSHR;
351 }
352 break;
353 case IN_WRKSHR:
354 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
355 case A_MP_ENDWORKSHARE:
356 state = NO_WRKSHR;
357 break;
358 case A_DO:
359 prevast = STD_AST(STD_PREV(std));
360 if (A_TYPEG(prevast) == A_COMMENT &&
361 A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(prevast)) == A_FORALL) {
362 ompast = gen_pdo(ast);
363 newstd = add_stmt_before(ompast, std);
364 if (parallel_depth > 1)
365 STD_PAR(newstd) = 1;
366 dolevel++;
367 state = IN_PDO;
368 ast_to_comment(ast);
369 } else {
370 /* probably an elemental intrinsic */
371 single = mk_stmt(A_MP_SINGLE, 0);
372 add_stmt_before(single, std);
373 dolevel++;
374 state = IN_SINGLE;
375 }
376 break;
377 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
378 single = mk_stmt(A_MP_SINGLE, 0);
379 add_stmt_before(single, std);
380 parallellevel++;
381 state = IN_PARALLEL;
382 break;
383 case A_MP_CRITICAL:
384 single = mk_stmt(A_MP_SINGLE, 0);
385 add_stmt_before(single, std);
386 state = IN_CRITICAL;
387 break;
388 case A_COMMENT:
389 switch (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(ast))) {
390 case A_WHERE:
391 wherelevel++;
392 break;
393 case A_ENDWHERE:
394 wherelevel--;
395 break;
396 }
397 break;
398 case A_ALLOC:
399 break;
400 case A_ASN:
401 lsptr = sym_of_ast(A_DESTG(ast));
402 if (wherelevel) {
403 if (HCCSYMG(lsptr)) {
404 THREADP(lsptr, 1);
405 break;
406 }
407 } else if (HCCSYMG(lsptr) && SCG(lsptr) == SC_PRIVATE) {
408 break;
409 }
410 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
411 default:
412 single = mk_stmt(A_MP_SINGLE, 0);
413 add_stmt_before(single, std);
414 state = IN_SINGLE;
415 break;
416 }
417 break;
418 case IN_PDO:
419 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
420 case A_DO:
421 dolevel++;
422 break;
423 case A_ENDDO:
424 if (--dolevel == 0) {
425 ompast = mk_stmt(A_MP_ENDPDO, 0);
426 ompstd = add_stmt_after(ompast, std);
427 add_stmt_after(mk_stmt(A_MP_BARRIER, 0), ompstd);
428 std = STD_NEXT(ompstd);
429 state = IN_WRKSHR;
430 ast_to_comment(ast);
431 }
432 break;
433 case A_COMMENT:
434 /* This case (WHERE or ENDWHERE in a DO) may never happen,
435 * but the comment STDs can sometimes get shuffled and may
436 * be out of order. Just to be safe */
437 switch (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(ast))) {
438 case A_WHERE:
439 wherelevel++;
440 break;
441 case A_ENDWHERE:
442 wherelevel--;
443 break;
444 }
445 break;
446 }
447 break;
448 case IN_SINGLE:
449 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
450 case A_MP_ENDWORKSHARE:
451 gen_endsingle(std, single, presinglebarrier);
452 presinglebarrier = 0;
453 state = NO_WRKSHR;
454 break;
455 case A_DO:
456 prevast = STD_AST(STD_PREV(std));
457 if (A_TYPEG(prevast) == A_COMMENT &&
458 A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(prevast)) == A_FORALL) {
459 gen_endsingle(STD_PREV(std), single, presinglebarrier);
460 presinglebarrier = 0;
461 ompast = gen_pdo(ast);
462 newstd = add_stmt_before(ompast, std);
463 if (parallel_depth > 1)
464 STD_PAR(newstd) = 1;
465 dolevel++;
466 state = IN_PDO;
467 ast_to_comment(ast);
468 } else {
469 dolevel++;
470 }
471 break;
472 case A_ENDDO:
473 dolevel--;
474 break;
475 case A_COMMENT:
476 switch (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(ast))) {
477 case A_FORALL:
478 gen_endsingle(std, single, presinglebarrier);
479 presinglebarrier = 0;
480 state = IN_WRKSHR;
481 break;
482 }
483 break;
484 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
485 state = IN_PARALLEL;
486 parallellevel++;
487 break;
488 case A_MP_CRITICAL:
489 state = IN_CRITICAL;
490 break;
491 }
492 break;
493 case IN_PARALLEL:
494 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
495 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
496 parallellevel++;
497 break;
498 case A_MP_ENDPARALLEL:
499 if (--parallellevel == 0) {
500 state = IN_SINGLE;
501 }
502 break;
503 }
504 if (newstd)
505 STD_PAR(newstd) = 1;
506
507 break;
508 case IN_CRITICAL:
509 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_MP_ENDCRITICAL) {
510 state = IN_SINGLE;
511 }
512 break;
513 }
514 }
515}
516
517static LOGICAL
518no_effect_forall(int std)
519{
520 int forall;
521 int asn;
522 int count;
523 int fusedstd;
524 int nd;
525 int i;
526
527 count = 0;
528 forall = STD_AST(std);
529 asn = A_IFSTMTG(forall);
530 if (A_SRCG(asn) == A_DESTG(asn))
531 count++;
532 nd = A_OPT1G(forall);
533 for (i = 0; i < FT_NFUSE(nd, 0); i++) {
534 fusedstd = FT_FUSEDSTD(nd, 0, i);
535 forall = STD_AST(fusedstd);
536 asn = A_IFSTMTG(forall);
537 if (A_SRCG(asn) == A_DESTG(asn))
538 count++;
539 }
540
541 if (count == FT_NFUSE(nd, 0) + 1) {
542 delete_stmt(std);
543 return TRUE;
544 }
545 return FALSE;
546}

548/*
549 * replace pghpf_lbound/pghpf_ubound(dim,descriptor)
550 */
551static int
552_pghpf_bound(int lbound, int ast)
553{
554 int argt, arg0, arg1, dim, ss[1], dtype, newast, offset;
555 newast = ast;
556 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
557 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
558 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
559 if ((A_TYPEG(arg1) == A_ID && DESCARRAYG(A_SPTRG(arg1))) ||
560 (A_TYPEG(arg1) == A_MEM && DESCARRAYG(A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(arg1))))) {
561 /* arg1 is a section descriptor */
562 dtype = A_DTYPEG(arg1);
563 if (A_ALIASG(arg0)) {
564 arg0 = A_ALIASG(arg0);
565 /* get constant value */
566 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg0));
567 offset = get_global_lower_index(dim - 1);
568 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)offset, DT_INT);
569 newast = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
570 if (!lbound) {
571 int a, b;
572 offset = get_global_extent_index(dim - 1);
573 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)offset, DT_INT);
574 b = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
575 a = mk_cval(1, astb.bnd.dtype);
576 b = mk_binop(OP_SUB, b, a, astb.bnd.dtype);
577 newast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, b, newast, astb.bnd.dtype);
578 }
579 } else {
580 /* dimension is not constant, compute offset */
581 int base;
582 int arg0decr = mk_binop(OP_SUB, arg0, astb.i1, DT_INT);
583 base = get_global_lower_index(0);
584 offset = get_global_lower_index(1);
585 offset = offset - base;
586 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)(offset), DT_INT);
587 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_MUL, arg0decr, ss[0], DT_INT);
588 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_ADD, mk_cval((INT)base, DT_INT), ss[0], DT_INT);
589 newast = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
590 if (!lbound) {
591 int a, b;
592 base = get_global_extent_index(0);
593 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)(offset), DT_INT);
594 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_MUL, arg0decr, ss[0], DT_INT);
595 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_ADD, mk_cval((INT)base, DT_INT), ss[0], DT_INT);
596 b = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
597 a = mk_cval(1, astb.bnd.dtype);
598 b = mk_binop(OP_SUB, b, a, astb.bnd.dtype);
599 newast = mk_binop(OP_ADD, b, newast, astb.bnd.dtype);
600 }
601 }
602 }
603 return newast;
604} /* _pghpf_bound */
605
606/*
607 * replace pghpf_size(dim,descriptor)/pghpf_extent(descriptor,dim)
608 */
609static int
610_pghpf_size(int size, int ast)
611{
612 int argt, arg0, arg1, dim, ss[1], dtype, newast, offset;
613 newast = ast;
614 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
615 if (size) {
616 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* dim */
617 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* section descriptor */
618 } else {
619 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* dim */
620 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* section descriptor */
621 }
622 if ((A_TYPEG(arg1) == A_ID && DESCARRAYG(A_SPTRG(arg1))) ||
623 (A_TYPEG(arg1) == A_MEM && DESCARRAYG(A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(arg1))))) {
624 /* arg1 is a section descriptor */
625 dtype = A_DTYPEG(arg1);
626 if (arg0 == astb.ptr0) {
627 /* global size */
628 ss[0] = mk_cval(get_desc_gsize_index(), DT_INT);
629 newast = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
630 } else if (A_ALIASG(arg0)) {
631 arg0 = A_ALIASG(arg0);
632 /* get constant value */
633 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg0));
634 offset = get_global_extent_index(dim - 1);
635 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)offset, DT_INT);
636 newast = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
637 } else {
638 /* dimension is not constant, compute offset */
639 int base;
640 int arg0decr = mk_binop(OP_SUB, arg0, astb.i1, DT_INT);
641 base = get_global_extent_index(0);
642 offset = get_global_extent_index(1);
643 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)(offset - base), DT_INT);
644 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_MUL, arg0decr, ss[0], DT_INT);
645 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_ADD, mk_cval((INT)base, DT_INT), ss[0], DT_INT);
646 newast = mk_subscr(arg1, ss, 1, DDTG(dtype));
647 }
648 }
649 return newast;
650} /* _pghpf_size */
651
652/*
653 * replace RTE_size(rank,dim,l1,u1,s1,l2,u2,s2,...)
654 */
655static int
656_RTE_size(int ast)
657{
658 int argt, arg0, arg1, argl, argu, args, rank, dim, newast, i;
659 newast = ast;
660 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
661 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* rank */
662 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* dim */
663 if (A_ALIASG(arg0)) {
664 arg0 = A_ALIASG(arg0);
665 rank = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg0));
666 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) == rank * 3 + 2) {
667 if (arg1 == astb.ptr0) {
668 newast = 0;
669 for (i = 0; i < rank; ++i) {
670 int a;
671 argl = ARGT_ARG(argt, i * 3 + 2);
672 argu = ARGT_ARG(argt, i * 3 + 3);
673 args = ARGT_ARG(argt, i * 3 + 4);
674 a = mk_binop(OP_SUB, argu, argl, A_DTYPEG(argl));
675 a = mk_binop(OP_ADD, a, args, A_DTYPEG(argl));
676 if (args != astb.i1 && args != astb.bnd.one) {
677 a = mk_binop(OP_DIV, a, args, A_DTYPEG(argl));
678 }
679 if (!newast) {
680 newast = a;
681 } else {
682 newast = mk_binop(OP_MUL, newast, a, A_DTYPEG(a));
683 }
684 }
685 } else if (A_ALIASG(arg1)) {
686 arg1 = A_ALIASG(arg1);
687 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg1));
688 if (dim >= 1 && dim <= rank) {
689 int a;
690 argl = ARGT_ARG(argt, (dim - 1) * 3 + 2);
691 argu = ARGT_ARG(argt, (dim - 1) * 3 + 3);
692 args = ARGT_ARG(argt, (dim - 1) * 3 + 4);
693 a = mk_binop(OP_SUB, argu, argl, A_DTYPEG(argl));
694 a = mk_binop(OP_ADD, a, args, A_DTYPEG(argl));
695 if (args != astb.i1 && args != astb.bnd.one) {
696 a = mk_binop(OP_DIV, a, args, A_DTYPEG(argl));
697 }
698 newast = a;
699 }
700 }
701 }
702 }
703 return newast;
704} /* _RTE_size */
705
706/*
707 * replace pgi_element_size( array )
708 */
709static int
710_pgi_element_size(int ast)
711{
712 int argt, arg0, sptr, dtype, ret;
713 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
714 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* variable or array */
715 sptr = memsym_of_ast(arg0);
716 if (sptr <= NOSYM) {
717 return astb.i0;
718 }
719 dtype = DDTG(DTYPEG(sptr));
720 ret = mk_cval(size_of(dtype), DT_INT);
721 return ret;
722} /* _pgi_element_size */
723
724/*
725 * replace pgi_kind( array )
726 */
727static int
728_pgi_kind(int ast)
729{
730 int argt, arg0, sptr, dtype, ret;
731 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
732 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* variable or array */
733 sptr = memsym_of_ast(arg0);
734 if (sptr <= NOSYM) {
735 return astb.i0;
736 }
737 dtype = DDTG(DTYPEG(sptr));
738 ret = mk_cval(dtype_to_arg(dtype), DT_INT);
739 return ret;
740} /* _pgi_kind */
741
742/*
743 * return an expression that gives the size of dimension i of a shape
744 * descriptor
745 */
746static int
747size_shape(int shape, int i)
748{
749 int a, mask;
750 int args = SHD_STRIDE(shape, i);
751 int argl = SHD_LWB(shape, i);
752 int argu = SHD_UPB(shape, i);
753 a = mk_binop(OP_SUB, argu, argl, astb.bnd.dtype);
754 a = mk_binop(OP_ADD, a, args, astb.bnd.dtype);
755 a = mk_binop(OP_DIV, a, args, astb.bnd.dtype);
756 /* 'a' is calculated as ((ub - lb + s) / s)
757 * which works for negative strides as well.
758 * Negative results are converted to zero.
759 */
760 mask = mk_binop(OP_GE, a, astb.bnd.zero, DT_LOG);
761 a = mk_merge(a, astb.bnd.zero, mask, astb.bnd.dtype);
762 if (astb.bnd.dtype != stb.user.dt_int) {
763 /* -i8: type of size is integer*8 so convert result */
764 a = mk_convert(a, stb.user.dt_int);
765 }
766 return a;
767} /* size_shape */
768
769/*
770 * replace size(array,dim) (from shape descriptor)
771 */
772static int
773_PDsize(int ast)
774{
775 int argt, argdim, arg, dim, ss[1], dtype, newast, offset, argsym, argsdsc;
776 int rank;
777 newast = ast;
778 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
779 arg = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* section descriptor */
780 argdim = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* dim */
781 argsym = 0;
782 argsdsc = 0;
783 if (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_ID) {
784 argsym = A_SPTRG(arg);
785 } else if (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_MEM) {
786 argsym = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(arg));
787 }
788 if (argsym) {
789 argsdsc = SDSCG(argsym);
790 if (!argsdsc || !DESCUSEDG(argsdsc) || !DESCARRAYG(argsdsc) ||
791 DTY(DTYPEG(argsym)) != TY_ARRAY) {
792 argsdsc = 0;
793 }
794 }
795 dtype = A_DTYPEG(arg);
796 if (argsdsc) {
797 /* arg is an array and has a section descriptor */
798 if (argdim == astb.ptr0) {
799 /* global size */
800 ss[0] = mk_cval(get_desc_gsize_index(), DT_INT);
801 } else if (A_ALIASG(argdim)) {
802 argdim = A_ALIASG(argdim);
803 /* get constant value */
804 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(argdim));
805 offset = get_global_extent_index(dim - 1);
806 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)offset, DT_INT);
807 } else {
808 /* dimension is not constant, compute offset */
809 int base;
810 base = get_global_extent_index(0);
811 offset = get_global_extent_index(1);
812 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)(offset - base), DT_INT);
813 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_MUL, argdim, ss[0], DT_INT);
814 ss[0] = mk_binop(OP_ADD, mk_cval(base - (offset - base), DT_INT), ss[0],
815 DT_INT);
816 }
817 newast = mk_subscr(mk_id(argsdsc), ss, 1, DTYPEG(argsdsc));
818 newast = check_member(arg, newast);
819 } else {
820 /* compute size from the shape descriptor */
821 int shape, i;
822
823 shape = A_SHAPEG(arg); /* this shape is always stride one */
824 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
825 if (argdim == astb.ptr0) {
826 /* global size */
827 newast = 0;
828 for (i = 0; i < rank; ++i) {
829 int a, args;
830 args = SHD_STRIDE(shape, i);
831 if (args != astb.i1 && args != astb.bnd.one) {
832 return ast;
833 }
834 a = size_shape(shape, i);
835 if (!newast) {
836 newast = a;
837 } else {
838 newast = mk_binop(OP_MUL, newast, a, A_DTYPEG(a));
839 }
840 }
841 } else if (A_ALIASG(argdim)) {
842 argdim = A_ALIASG(argdim);
843 /* get constant value */
844 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(argdim));
845 newast = size_shape(shape, dim - 1);
846 } else {
847 /* dimension is not constant, give up */
848 newast = ast;
849 }
850 }
851 return newast;
852} /* _PDsize */
853
854/**
855 * \brief Used to simplify PD_lbound or PD_ubound call ast nodes to the value
856 * from shape descriptor of adjustable array.
857 * \param lbound Flag which represents whether this is a call to lbound routine.
858 * When set to zero, it means call is to ubound.
859 * \param ast The AST node representing the call to lbound/ubound.
860 * \return AST node representing value extracted from shape.
861 */
862static int
863_PDbound(int lbound, int ast)
864{
865 int argt, argdim, arg, dim;
866 int rank, shape, bound;
867 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
868 arg = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
869 argdim = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
870 /* The implementation requires that argument is an array and that dimension argument
871 is a constant. */
872 if (A_TYPEG(arg) == A_ID &&
873 DTY(A_DTYPEG(arg)) == TY_ARRAY &&
874 A_ALIASG(argdim)) {
875 shape = A_SHAPEG(arg);
876 /* Replacement of bound call can only happen if shape is known */
877 if (shape) {
878 rank = SHD_NDIM(shape);
879 argdim = A_ALIASG(argdim);
880 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(argdim));
881 if (lbound) {
882 bound = SHD_LWB(shape, dim - 1);
883 } else {
884 bound = SHD_UPB(shape, dim - 1);
885 }
886 return bound;
887 }
888 }
889
890 return ast;
891} /* _PDbound */
892
893/*
894 * replace RTE_lbound/RTE_ubound(rank,dim,b1,b2,b3,...)
895 */
896static int
897_RTE_bound(int lbound, int ast)
898{
899 int argt, arg0, arg1, rank, dim, newast;
900 newast = ast;
901 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
902 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* rank */
903 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* dim */
904 if (A_ALIASG(arg0)) {
905 arg0 = A_ALIASG(arg0);
906 rank = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg0));
907 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) == rank + 2) {
908 if (A_ALIASG(arg1)) {
909 arg1 = A_ALIASG(arg1);
910 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg1));
911 if (dim >= 1 && dim <= rank) {
912 newast = ARGT_ARG(argt, (dim - 1) + 2 + (lbound ? 0 : 1));
913 }
914 }
915 }
916 }
917 return newast;
918} /* _RTE_bound */
919
920/*
921 * replace RTE_lb/RTE_ub(rank,dim,l1,u1,l1,u2,...)
922 */
923static int
924_RTE_xb(int lbound, int ast, int rdt, int dolong)
925{
926 int argt, arg0, arg1, rank, dim, newast;
927 newast = ast;
928 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
929 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* rank */
930 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* dim */
931 if (A_ALIASG(arg0)) {
932 arg0 = A_ALIASG(arg0);
933 rank = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg0));
934 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) == 2 * rank + 2) {
935 if (A_ALIASG(arg1)) {
936 arg1 = A_ALIASG(arg1);
937 dim = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg1));
938 if (dim >= 1 && dim <= rank) {
939 int tsource, fsource, mask; /* merge arguemnts */
940 int ub, lb;
941 lb = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2 * (dim - 1) + 2);
942 ub = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2 * (dim - 1) + 2 + 1);
943 if (lbound) {
944 tsource = lb;
945 fsource = astb.bnd.one;
946 } else {
947 tsource = ub;
948 fsource = astb.bnd.zero;
949 }
950 mask = mk_binop(OP_LE, lb, ub, DT_LOG);
951 newast = mk_merge(tsource, fsource, mask, dolong ? DT_INT8 : DT_INT);
952 if (rdt) {
953 newast = mk_convert(newast, rdt);
954 }
955 }
956 }
957 }
958 }
959 return newast;
960} /* _RTE_xb */
961
962/*
963 * replace RTE_uba and RTE_lba
964 */
965static int
966_RTE_ba(int lbound, int ast)
967{
968 int argt, arg0, arg1, rank, dim, lhs, rhs, ss[1];
969 int ub, lb, newif, cmp, newstd;
970
971 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
972 arg0 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0); /* result array */
973 arg1 = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1); /* rank */
974 if (A_ALIASG(arg1)) {
975 arg1 = A_ALIASG(arg1);
976 rank = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(arg1));
977 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) == rank * 2 + 2) {
978 for (dim = 1; dim <= rank; dim++) {
979 lb = ARGT_ARG(argt, (dim - 1) * 2 + 2);
980 ub = ARGT_ARG(argt, (dim - 1) * 2 + 3);
981 ss[0] = mk_cval((INT)dim, DT_INT);
982 lhs = mk_subscr(arg0, ss, 1, DT_INT);
983
984 if (dim == rank && ub == astb.ptr0) {
985 /*
986 * Special case for F77 assumed size arrays which
987 * have no upper bound in the last dimension.
988 */
989 rhs = (lbound ? lb : astb.bnd.zero);
990 insert_assign(lhs, rhs, beforestd);
991 } else if (lbound && (lb == astb.i1 || lb == astb.bnd.one)) {
992 /*
993 * Special case for constant one lower bound.
994 * No need for the if-then-else.
995 */
996 insert_assign(lhs, lb, beforestd);
997 } else {
998 /* if (lb <= ub) ... */
999 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
1000 cmp = mk_binop(OP_LE, lb, ub, DT_LOG);
1001 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1002 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1003 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1004 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1005 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1006 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1007
1008 /* lhs = (lbound ? lb : ub) */
1009 rhs = (lbound ? lb : ub);
1010 insert_assign(lhs, rhs, beforestd);
1011
1012 /* else */
1013 newif = mk_stmt(A_ELSE, 0);
1014 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1015 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1016 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1017 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1018 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1019
1020 /* lhs = (lbound ? 1 : 0) */
1021 rhs = (lbound ? astb.bnd.one : astb.bnd.zero);
1022 insert_assign(lhs, rhs, beforestd);
1023
1024 /* end if */
1025 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
1026 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1027 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1028 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1029 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1030 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1031 }
1032 }
1033 ast_to_comment(ast);
1034 }
1035 }
1036 return ast;
1037}
1038
1039/*
1040 * return operand of %val(), else just return the ast
1041 */
1042static int
1043value(int ast)
1044{
1045 if (ast > 0 && A_TYPEG(ast) == A_UNOP &&
1046 (A_OPTYPEG(ast) == OP_VAL || A_OPTYPEG(ast) == OP_BYVAL))
1047 ast = A_LOPG(ast);
1048 if (ast > 0 && A_ALIASG(ast))
1049 ast = A_ALIASG(ast);
1050 return ast;
1051} /* value */
1052
1053/*
1054 * put value in a symbol if it's an expression
1055 */
1056static int
1057symvalue(int ast, char c, int num, int *ptemp, int var, int sdsc)
1058{
1059 int temp, newasn, newstd, a;
1060 ast = value(ast);
1061 if (!var && (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID || A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CNST))
1062 return ast;
1063 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_SUBSCR && A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(ast)) == A_ID &&
1064 (sdsc > 0 ? A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast)) == sdsc
1065 : DESCARRAYG(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(ast)))))
1066 return ast;
1067 if (*ptemp == 0) {
1068 *ptemp = temp = getnewccsymf(ST_VAR, ".c%d_%d", num, newsymnum++);
1069 SCP(temp, SC_LOCAL);
1070 DTYPEP(temp, astb.bnd.dtype);
1071 if (STD_PAR(beforestd) || STD_TASK(beforestd))
1072 SCP(temp, SC_PRIVATE);
1073 }
1074 a = mk_id(*ptemp);
1075 if (ast == a)
1076 return ast;
1077 newasn = mk_stmt(A_ASN, 0);
1078 A_DESTP(newasn, a);
1079 A_SRCP(newasn, ast);
1080 newstd = add_stmt_before(newasn, beforestd);
1081 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1082 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1083 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1084 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1085 return a;
1086} /* symvalue */
1087
1088/*
1089 * see above
1090 */
1091static void
1092_simple_replacements(int ast, int *pany)
1093{
1094 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_FUNC || A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CALL) {
1095 int lop;
1096 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
1097 if (lop && A_TYPEG(lop) == A_ID) {
1098 int fsptr;
1099 fsptr = A_SPTRG(lop);
1100 if (HCCSYMG(fsptr) && STYPEG(fsptr) == ST_PROC) {
1101 /* compiler created function */
1102 int newast;
1103 char *fname;
1104 int in_device_code;
1105 fname = SYMNAME(fsptr);
1106 newast = ast;
1107 in_device_code = 0;
1108 if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lboundDsc)) == 0) {
1109 newast = _pghpf_bound(1, ast);
1110 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_uboundDsc)) == 0) {
1111 newast = _pghpf_bound(0, ast);
1112 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_extent)) == 0) {
1113 newast = _pghpf_size(0, ast);
1114 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_sizeDsc)) == 0) {
1115 newast = ARGT_ARG(A_ARGSG(ast), 1);
1116 if (A_TYPEG(newast) == A_ID && ASSUMRANKG(A_SPTRG(newast))) {
1117 return;
1118 }
1119 newast = _pghpf_size(1, ast);
1120 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_size)) == 0) {
1121 newast = _RTE_size(ast);
1122 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lbound)) == 0) {
1123 newast = _RTE_bound(1, ast);
1124 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_ubound)) == 0) {
1125 newast = _RTE_bound(0, ast);
1126 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lba)) == 0) {
1127 if (in_device_code || XBIT(137, 0x20))
1128 newast = _RTE_ba(1, ast);
1129 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_uba)) == 0) {
1130 if (in_device_code || XBIT(137, 0x20))
1131 newast = _RTE_ba(0, ast);
1132 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_extent)) == 0) {
1133 newast = _pghpf_size(0, ast);
1134 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_sizeDsc)) == 0) {
1135 newast = _pghpf_size(1, ast);
1136 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_size)) == 0) {
1137 newast = _RTE_size(ast);
1138 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lbound)) == 0) {
1139 newast = _RTE_bound(1, ast);
1140 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_ubound)) == 0) {
1141 newast = _RTE_bound(0, ast);
1142 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lba)) == 0) {
1143 if (in_device_code || XBIT(137, 0x20))
1144 newast = _RTE_ba(1, ast);
1145 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_uba)) == 0) {
1146 if (in_device_code || XBIT(137, 0x20))
1147 newast = _RTE_ba(0, ast);
1148 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_lb)) == 0) {
1149 /* Last arg:
1150 * large arrays || ub/lb retval is 8 byte int || int is 8 byte
1151 */
1152 newast = _RTE_xb(1, ast, 0,
1153 XBIT(68, 0x1) || XBIT(86, 0x2) || XBIT(128, 0x10));
1154 } else if (strcmp(fname, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_ub)) == 0) {
1155 /* Last arg:
1156 * large arrays || ub/lb retval is 8 byte int || int is 8 byte
1157 */
1158 newast = _RTE_xb(0, ast, 0,
1159 XBIT(68, 0x1) || XBIT(86, 0x2) || XBIT(128, 0x10));
1160 }
1161 if (newast != ast) {
1162 if (A_DTYPEG(newast) != A_DTYPEG(ast))
1163 newast = mk_convert(newast, A_DTYPEG(ast));
1164 ast_replace(ast, newast);
1165 *pany = *pany + 1;
1166 }
1167 } else if (XBIT(57, 0x4000000)) {
1168 int newast;
1169 char *fname;
1170 fname = SYMNAME(fsptr);
1171 newast = ast;
1172 if (strcmp(fname, "pgi_element_size") == 0) {
1173 newast = _pgi_element_size(ast);
1174 } else if (strcmp(fname, "pgi_kind") == 0) {
1175 newast = _pgi_kind(ast);
1176 }
1177 if (newast != ast) {
1178 if (A_DTYPEG(newast) != A_DTYPEG(ast))
1179 newast = mk_convert(newast, A_DTYPEG(ast));
1180 ast_replace(ast, newast);
1181 *pany = *pany + 1;
1182 }
1183 }
1184 }
1185 } else if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_INTR) {
1186 int lop;
1187 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
1188 if (lop && A_TYPEG(lop) == A_ID) {
1189 int fsptr;
1190 fsptr = A_SPTRG(lop);
1191 if (STYPEG(fsptr) == ST_PD) {
1192 /* predeclared procedure */
1193 int newast;
1194 newast = ast;
1195 if (PDNUMG(fsptr) == PD_size) {
1196 /* size(array,dim) ==> array$sd( extent(dim) ) if there is a $sd
1197 * ==> ubound(array,dim)-lbound(array,dim)+1 else
1198 * size(array,<0>) ==> array$sd( gsize ) if there is a $sd
1199 * ==> product(ubound(array,dim)-lbound(array,dim)+1)
1200 *else
1201 * size(expr,dim) ==> ubound(shape,dim)-lbound(shape,dim)+1
1202 * size(expr,dim) ==> product(ubound(shape,dim)-lbound(shape,dim)+1)
1203 */
1204 newast = _PDsize(ast);
1205 } else if (PDNUMG(fsptr) == PD_lbound) {
1206 newast = _PDbound(1, ast);
1207 } else if (PDNUMG(fsptr) == PD_ubound) {
1208 newast = _PDbound(0, ast);
1209 }
1210 if (newast != ast) {
1211 if (A_DTYPEG(newast) != A_DTYPEG(ast))
1212 newast = mk_convert(newast, A_DTYPEG(ast));
1213 ast_replace(ast, newast);
1214 *pany = *pany + 1;
1215 }
1216 }
1217 }
1218 }
1219} /* _simple_replacements */
1220
1221static void
1222convert_simple(void)
1223{
1224 int std, stdnext;
1225 int ast, any;
1226
1227 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = stdnext) {
1228 stdnext = STD_NEXT(std);
1229 ast = STD_AST(std);
1230 ast_visit(1, 1);
1231 any = 0; /* any replacements found? */
1232 beforestd = std;
1233 ast_traverse(ast, NULL, _simple_replacements, &any);
1234 if (any) {
1235 ast = ast_rewrite(ast);
1236 STD_AST(std) = ast;
1237 A_STDP(ast, std);
1238 }
1239 ast_unvisit();
1240 }
1241} /* convert_simple */
1242
1243/*
1244 * check that this is a single subscript with constant value as given
1245 */
1246static int
1247check_subscript(int ast, int value)
1248{
1249 int asd, ss, val;
1250 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
1251 if (ASD_NDIM(asd) != 1)
1252 return 0;
1253 ss = ASD_SUBS(asd, 0);
1254 if (A_TYPEG(ss) != A_CNST)
1255 return 0;
1256 val = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(ss));
1257 if (value != val)
1258 return 0;
1259 return 1;
1260} /* check_subscript */
1261
1262/*
1263 * check that the constant value matches what we expect
1264 */
1265static int
1266check_value(int ast, int value)
1267{
1268 int val;
1269 if (A_TYPEG(ast) != A_CNST)
1270 return 0;
1271 val = get_int_cval(A_SPTRG(ast));
1272 if (value != val)
1273 return 0;
1274 return 1;
1275} /* check_value */
1276
1277/*
1278 * for RTE_sect calls, see if the lower bound / upper bound / stride
1279 * arguments for this dimension are the corresponding full dimension.
1280 * lower bound = section descriptor(lbound)
1281 * upper bound = section descriptor(ubound) OR
1282 * upper bound = section descriptor(lbound) + (section descriptor(extent)-1)
1283 * stride = 1
1284 */
1285static int
1286full_dimension(int astlower, int astupper, int aststride, int dim)
1287{
1288 int sdsc = 0;
1289 if (!check_value(aststride, 1))
1290 return 0;
1291 if (A_TYPEG(astlower) == A_SUBSCR) {
1292 if (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(astlower)) != A_ID)
1293 return 0;
1294 sdsc = A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(astlower));
1295 if (!DESCARRAYG(sdsc))
1296 return 0;
1297 if (!check_subscript(astlower, get_global_lower_index(dim)))
1298 return 0;
1299 } else {
1300 return 0;
1301 }
1302 if (A_TYPEG(astupper) == A_SUBSCR) {
1303 if (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(astupper)) != A_ID)
1304 return 0;
1305 if (A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(astupper)) != sdsc)
1306 return 0;
1307 if (!check_subscript(astupper, get_global_upper_index(dim)))
1308 return 0;
1309 } else if (A_TYPEG(astupper) == A_BINOP && A_OPTYPEG(astupper) == OP_ADD) {
1310 int astleft, astright;
1311 astleft = A_LOPG(astupper);
1312 astright = A_ROPG(astupper);
1313 if (A_TYPEG(astleft) == A_SUBSCR) {
1314 if (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(astleft)) != A_ID)
1315 return 0;
1316 if (A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(astleft)) != sdsc)
1317 return 0;
1318 if (!check_subscript(astleft, get_global_lower_index(dim)))
1319 return 0;
1320 } else {
1321 return 0;
1322 }
1323 if (A_TYPEG(astright) == A_BINOP && A_OPTYPEG(astright) == OP_SUB) {
1324 astleft = A_LOPG(astright);
1325 astright = A_ROPG(astright);
1326 if (A_TYPEG(astleft) == A_SUBSCR) {
1327 if (A_TYPEG(A_LOPG(astleft)) != A_ID)
1328 return 0;
1329 if (A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(astleft)) != sdsc)
1330 return 0;
1331 if (!check_subscript(astleft, get_global_extent_index(dim)))
1332 return 0;
1333 } else {
1334 return 0;
1335 }
1336 if (!check_value(astright, 1))
1337 return 0;
1338 } else {
1339 return 0;
1340 }
1341 } else {
1342 return 0;
1343 }
1344 return sdsc;
1345} /* full_dimension */
1346
1347/*
1348 * insert an assignment statement
1349 */
1350static void
1351insert_assign(int lhs, int rhs, int beforestd)
1352{
1353 int newasn, newstd;
1354 if (lhs == rhs)
1355 return;
1356 newasn = MKASSN(lhs, rhs);
1357 newstd = add_stmt_before(newasn, beforestd);
1358 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1359 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1360 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1361 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1362} /* insert_assign */
1363
1364/*
1365 * replace RTE_sect calls
1366 * RTE_sect( newsd, oldsd, dims, [lower, upper, stride,]... flags )
1367 *
1368 * newsd.rank = rank -- must be constant
1369 * newsd.kind = oldsd.kind
1370 * newsd.bytelen = oldsd.bytelen
1371 * flagstemp = oldsd.flags -- handle constant case here
1372 * newsd.lsize = oldsd.lsize
1373 * newsd.gbase = oldsd.gbase
1374 * d=0
1375 * if flagstemp & SECTZBASE
1376 * lbasetemp = 1
1377 * else
1378 * lbasetemp = oldsd.lbase
1379 * endif
1380 * gsizetemp = 1
1381 * for r = 0 to rank-1 do
1382 * if flags & (1<<r) then -- section dimension
1383 * upper = oldsd.upper[r]
1384 * lower = oldsd.lower[r]
1385 * stride = oldsd.stride[r]
1386 * set extent=upper-lower+stride
1387 * if stride == -1 then extent = -extent
1388 * elseif stride != 1 then extent /= stride; endif
1389 * if flags & SECTZBASE then
1390 * if extent < 0 then extent = 0 endif
1391 * newsd[d].lbound = 1
1392 * newsd[d].ubound = extent
1393 * newsd[d].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride
1394 * lbasetemp -= newsd[d].lstride
1395 * else
1396 * if extent < 0 then extent = 0; upper = lower-1; stride=1; endif
1397 * newsd[d].extent = extent
1398 * if flags & NOREINDEX and stride == 1 then
1399 * newsd[d].lbound = lower
1400 * newsd[d].ubound = upper
1401 * set myoffset=0
1402 * else
1403 * newsd[d].lbound = 1
1404 * newsd[d].ubound = extent
1405 * set myoffset = lower-stride
1406 * endif
1407 * newsd[d].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride
1408 * lbasetemp += myoffset * oldsd[r].lstride
1409 * endif
1410 * newsd[d].sstride = 1
1411 * newsd[d].soffset = 0
1412 * if newsd[d].lstride != gsizetemp then reset flagstemp -= SEQUENTIAL_SECTION
1413 *endif
1414 * set gsizetemp *= extent
1415 * ++d
1416 * else
1417 * set lidx = oldsd[r].sstride * oldsd[r].lbound + oldsd[r].soffset =
1418 *oldsd[r].lbound
1419 * set k = oldsd[r].lstride * ( lidx - oldsd[r].lbound )
1420 * = oldsd[r].lstride * ( lower - oldsd[r].lbound )
1421 * = oldsd[r].lstride * lower - oldsd[r].lstride * oldsd[r].lbound
1422 * lbasetemp += k + (oldsd[r].lstride * oldsd[r].lbound)
1423 * += oldsd[r].lstride * lower - oldsd[r].lstride * oldsd[r].lbound
1424 * + (oldsd[r].lstride * oldsd[r].lbound)
1425 * += oldsd[r].lstride * lower
1426 * endif
1427 * endfor
1428 * newsd.flags = flagstemp
1429 * newsd.lbase = lbasetemp
1430 * newsd.tag = DESCRIPTOR
1431 */
1432
1433#define VALUE_ARGT_ARG(a, b) value(ARGT_ARG(a, b))
1434
1435static int
1436_sect(int ast, int i8)
1437{
1438#define TAGDESC 35
1439#define SECTZBASE 0x00400000
1440#define SEQSECTION 0x20000000
1441#define TEMPLATE 0x00010000
1442 int argt, newargt, f, funcast;
1443 int astoldsd, astnewsd, astrank, astflags;
1444 int sptroldsd, sptrnewsd;
1445 int rank, flags, dims;
1446 int newstd, gsizeast, astgsize, lbaseast, astlbase;
1447 int flagstemp = 0, flagsast = 0, flagsseq = 1, gsizetemp = 0, lbasetemp = 0;
1448 int needgsize;
1449 int lowertemp = 0, uppertemp = 0, stridetemp = 0, extenttemp = 0;
1450 int myoffset = 0, astoffset = 0;
1451 int newif, cmp, mightbesequential = 1, leading, leadingfull,
1452 computesequential;
1453 int r, d;
1454 int dtype = DT_INT;
1455 if (i8)
1456 dtype = DT_INT8;
1457 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
1458 astnewsd = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
1459 astoldsd = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
1460 if (A_TYPEG(astnewsd) != A_ID || A_TYPEG(astoldsd) != A_ID)
1461 return 0;
1462 sptrnewsd = A_SPTRG(astnewsd);
1463 sptroldsd = A_SPTRG(astoldsd);
1464 if (CLASSG(sptrnewsd) || CLASSG(sptroldsd))
1465 return 0;
1466 astrank = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 2);
1467 if (astrank <= 0)
1468 return 0;
1469 if (A_TYPEG(astrank) != A_CNST)
1470 return 0;
1471 rank = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(astrank));
1472 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) != 3 * rank + 4)
1473 return 0;
1474 astflags = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 3 * rank + 3);
1475 if (astflags <= 0)
1476 return 0;
1477 if (A_TYPEG(astflags) != A_CNST)
1478 return 0;
1479 flags = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(astflags));
1480 if (flags & 0x100) /* BOGUSFLAG */
1481 return 0;
1482 /* output dimensions is the pop count of flags */
1483 dims = (flags & 0x55) + ((flags >> 1) & 0x15);
1484 dims = (dims & 0x33) + ((dims >> 2) & 0x13);
1485 dims += (dims >> 4);
1486 dims = dims & 0xf;
1487 if (dims > rank || dims <= 0)
1488 return 0;
1489 needgsize = 0;
1490 if (XBIT(47, 0x1000000) || SCG(sptroldsd) == SC_CMBLK || gbl.internal == 1 ||
1491 (gbl.internal > 1 && INTERNALG(sptroldsd)) || ARGG(sptroldsd))
1492 needgsize = 1;
1493
1494 /* set newsd.rank = rank */
1495 insert_assign(get_desc_rank(sptrnewsd), mk_isz_cval(dims, astb.bnd.dtype),
1496 beforestd);
1497 /* copy newsd.kind = oldsd.kind */
1498 insert_assign(get_kind(sptrnewsd), get_kind(sptroldsd), beforestd);
1499/* copy newsd.len = oldsd.len */
1500#ifdef SDSCCONTIGG
1501 if (SDSCCONTIGG(sptroldsd)) {
1502 insert_assign(get_byte_len(sptrnewsd),
1503 mk_isz_cval(BYTELENG(sptroldsd), astb.bnd.dtype), beforestd);
1504 } else
1505#endif
1506 {
1507 insert_assign(get_byte_len(sptrnewsd), get_byte_len(sptroldsd), beforestd);
1508 }
1509 /* copy flags_temp = oldsd.flags */
1510 flagsast = get_desc_flags(sptroldsd);
1511 flagsseq = 1;
1512 /* copy newsd.gbase = oldsd.gbase */
1513 insert_assign(get_gbase(sptrnewsd), get_gbase(sptroldsd), beforestd);
1514 if (XBIT(49, 0x100) && !XBIT(49, 0x80000000) && !XBIT(68, 0x1)) {
1515 /* pointers are two ints long */
1516 insert_assign(get_gbase2(sptrnewsd), get_gbase2(sptroldsd), beforestd);
1517 }
1518 /* r runs through old rank; d runs through new dims */
1519 d = 0;
1520 if (flags & SECTZBASE) {
1521 /* set lbasetemp = 1 */
1522 lbaseast = astb.bnd.one;
1523 } else {
1524 /* copy lbasetemp = oldsd.lbase */
1525 lbaseast = get_xbase(sptroldsd);
1526 }
1527
1528 /* might this be a sequential section?
1529 * only if all leading dimensions are sections with stride == 1
1530 */
1531 leading = 1;
1532 leadingfull = 1;
1533 computesequential = 1;
1534 for (r = 0; r < rank; ++r) {
1535 if (!(flags & (1 << r))) {
1536 /* nonvector dimension */
1537 leading = 0;
1538 needgsize = 1;
1539 } else {
1540 int aststride, astlower, astupper;
1541 if (!leading) {
1542 /* vector dimension after nonvector dimension
1543 * like a(:,2,:) can't be sequential */
1544 mightbesequential = 0;
1545 computesequential = 0;
1546 needgsize = 1;
1547 break;
1548 }
1549 aststride = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 5 + 3 * r);
1550 if (!check_value(aststride, 1)) {
1551 /* a(1:n:2) can't be sequential */
1552 mightbesequential = 0;
1553 computesequential = 0;
1554 needgsize = 1;
1555 break;
1556 }
1557 if (!leadingfull) {
1558 /* a(:,1:n,:) might be sequential */
1559 computesequential = 1;
1560 needgsize = 1;
1561 }
1562 astlower = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 3 + 3 * r);
1563 astupper = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 4 + 3 * r);
1564 if (!full_dimension(astlower, astupper, aststride, r)) {
1565 leadingfull = 0;
1566 needgsize = 1;
1567 }
1568 }
1569 }
1570 if (computesequential)
1571 needgsize = 1;
1572 if (needgsize) {
1573 /* create temp to hold global size */
1574 gsizetemp = getnewccsymf(ST_VAR, ".g%d_%d", ast, newsymnum++);
1575 SCP(gsizetemp, SC_LOCAL);
1576 DTYPEP(gsizetemp, astb.bnd.dtype);
1577 if (STD_PAR(beforestd) || STD_TASK(beforestd)) {
1578 SCP(gsizetemp, SC_PRIVATE);
1579 }
1580 gsizeast = astb.bnd.one;
1581 }
1582 if (!mightbesequential && flagsseq) {
1583 f = SEQSECTION;
1584 f = ~f;
1585 newargt = mk_argt(2);
1586 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = flagsast;
1587 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = mk_isz_cval(f, dtype);
1588 flagsast = mk_func_node(A_INTR, mk_id(intast_sym[I_AND]), 2, newargt);
1589 A_OPTYPEP(flagsast, I_AND);
1590 A_DTYPEP(flagsast, dtype);
1591 flagsseq = 0;
1592 }
1593 for (r = 0; r < rank; ++r) {
1594 int astlower = 0, astupper = 0, aststride = 0, astextent = 0, sdsc;
1595 ISZ_T extent, stride;
1596 astlower = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 3 + 3 * r);
1597 astupper = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 4 + 3 * r);
1598 aststride = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, 5 + 3 * r);
1599 if (flags & (1 << r)) {
1600 if ((sdsc = full_dimension(astlower, astupper, aststride, r))) {
1601 astlower = symvalue(astlower, 'l', sptrnewsd, &lowertemp, 0, 0);
1602 if ((flags & NOREINDEX) && XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1603 /* going to need the upper bound */
1604 astupper =
1605 symvalue(astupper, 'u', sptrnewsd, &uppertemp, 0, sptrnewsd);
1606 }
1607 astextent = get_extent(sdsc, r);
1608 } else {
1609 astlower = symvalue(astlower, 'l', sptrnewsd, &lowertemp, 0, 0);
1610 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1611 astupper =
1612 symvalue(astupper, 'u', sptrnewsd, &uppertemp, 0, sptrnewsd);
1613 }
1614 aststride = symvalue(aststride, 's', sptrnewsd, &stridetemp, 0, 0);
1615 /* section dimension */
1616 if (astlower == aststride) {
1617 astextent = astupper;
1618 } else {
1619 /* this is carefully orchestrated.
1620 * if the RTE_sect call was to create a section of another
1621 * descriptor, for instance when we pass a section of an
1622 * array to a subprogram, the call looks like:
1623 * call RTE_sect(..,a$sd(lower),extent+(a$sd(lower)-a$sd(stride))..
1624 * where the upper bound of the section is lower+extent-stride.
1625 * here, we want to organize the expression to cancel out the
1626 * (lower-stride) if we can. */
1627 astextent =
1628 mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, aststride, A_DTYPEG(aststride));
1629 astextent =
1630 mk_binop(OP_SUB, astupper, astextent, A_DTYPEG(astextent));
1631 }
1632 astextent =
1633 symvalue(astextent, 'x', sptrnewsd, &extenttemp, 0, sptrnewsd);
1634 if (A_TYPEG(astextent) == A_CNST && A_TYPEG(aststride) == A_CNST) {
1635 extent = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(astextent));
1636 stride = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(aststride));
1637 if (stride == -1) {
1638 extent = -extent;
1639 } else {
1640 extent = extent / stride;
1641 }
1642 if (extent <= 0) {
1643 stride = 1;
1644 aststride = astb.bnd.one;
1645 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1646 astupper =
1647 mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, astb.bnd.one, A_DTYPEG(astlower));
1648 }
1649 extent = 0;
1650 astextent = astb.bnd.zero;
1651 } else {
1652 astextent = mk_isz_cval(extent, A_DTYPEG(astextent));
1653 }
1654 } else {
1655 if (A_TYPEG(aststride) == A_CNST) {
1656 stride = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(aststride));
1657 if (stride == -1) {
1658 astextent = mk_unop(OP_NEG, astextent, A_DTYPEG(astextent));
1659 } else if (stride != 1) {
1660 astextent =
1661 mk_binop(OP_DIV, astextent, aststride, A_DTYPEG(astextent));
1662 }
1663 astextent =
1664 symvalue(astextent, 'x', sptrnewsd, &extenttemp, 1, sptrnewsd);
1665 } else {
1666 /* generate code to do the divide */
1667 /* if( stride .eq. -1 ) then */
1668
1669 if (A_TYPEG(astextent) == A_CNST) {
1670 astextent = symvalue(astextent, 'x', sptrnewsd, &extenttemp, 1,
1671 sptrnewsd);
1672 }
1673 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
1674 cmp = mk_binop(OP_EQ, aststride,
1675 mk_isz_cval(-1, A_DTYPEG(aststride)), DT_LOG);
1676 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1677 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1678 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1679 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1680 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1681 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1682 /* extent = -extent */
1683 insert_assign(astextent,
1684 mk_unop(OP_NEG, astextent, A_DTYPEG(astextent)),
1685 beforestd);
1686 /* else if( stride .ne. 1 )then */
1687 newif = mk_stmt(A_ELSEIF, 0);
1688 cmp = mk_binop(OP_NE, aststride, astb.bnd.one, DT_LOG);
1689 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1690 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1691 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1692 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1693 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1694 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1695 /* extent = extent / stride */
1696 insert_assign(astextent, mk_binop(OP_DIV, astextent, aststride,
1697 A_DTYPEG(astextent)),
1698 beforestd);
1699 /* endif */
1700 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
1701 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1702 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1703 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1704 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1705 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1706 }
1707 /* make sure upper bound is in a variable */
1708 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1709 astupper =
1710 symvalue(astupper, 'u', sptrnewsd, &uppertemp, 1, sptrnewsd);
1711 }
1712 /* if( extent < 0 )then */
1713 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
1714 cmp = mk_binop(OP_LE, astextent, astb.bnd.zero, DT_LOG);
1715 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1716 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1717 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1718 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1719 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1720 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1721 /* extent = 0 */
1722 insert_assign(astextent, astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
1723 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1724 /* upper = lower-1 */
1725 insert_assign(astupper, mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, astb.bnd.one,
1726 A_DTYPEG(astlower)),
1727 beforestd);
1728 }
1729 /* endif */
1730 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
1731 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1732 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1733 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1734 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1735 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1736 }
1737 }
1738 /* newsd[d].extent = extent */
1739 insert_assign(get_extent(sptrnewsd, d), astextent, beforestd);
1740
1741 if (flags & SECTZBASE) {
1742 /* newsd[d].lbound = 1 */
1743 insert_assign(get_global_lower(sptrnewsd, d), astb.bnd.one, beforestd);
1744 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1745 /* newsd[d].ubound = extent */
1746 insert_assign(get_global_upper(sptrnewsd, d), astextent, beforestd);
1747 }
1748 /* newsd[d].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride */
1749 insert_assign(get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, d),
1750 mk_binop(OP_MUL, aststride,
1751 get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1752 A_DTYPEG(aststride)),
1753 beforestd);
1754 /* lbasetemp -= newsd[d].lstride */
1755 astlbase =
1756 mk_binop(OP_SUB, lbaseast, get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, d),
1757 A_DTYPEG(aststride));
1758 lbaseast = symvalue(astlbase, 'b', sptroldsd, &lbasetemp, 1, 0);
1759 } else if ((flags & NOREINDEX) && A_TYPEG(aststride) == A_CNST &&
1760 CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(aststride)) == 1) {
1761 /* newsd[d].lbound = lower */
1762 insert_assign(get_global_lower(sptrnewsd, d), astlower, beforestd);
1763 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1764 /* newsd[d].ubound = upper */
1765 insert_assign(get_global_upper(sptrnewsd, d), astupper, beforestd);
1766 }
1767 /* newsd[d].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride */
1768 insert_assign(get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, d),
1769 mk_binop(OP_MUL, aststride,
1770 get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1771 A_DTYPEG(aststride)),
1772 beforestd);
1773 } else if ((flags & NOREINDEX)) {
1774 /* if stride == 1 then */
1775 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
1776 cmp = mk_binop(OP_EQ, aststride, astb.bnd.one, DT_LOG);
1777 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1778 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1779 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1780 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1781 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1782 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1783 /* newsd[d].lbound = lower */
1784 insert_assign(get_global_lower(sptrnewsd, d), astlower, beforestd);
1785 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1786 /* newsd[d].ubound = upper */
1787 insert_assign(get_global_upper(sptrnewsd, d), astupper, beforestd);
1788 }
1789 /* set myoffset=0 */
1790 if (myoffset == 0) {
1791 myoffset = getnewccsymf(ST_VAR, ".o%d_%d", ast, newsymnum++);
1792 astlower = symvalue(astlower, 'l', sptrnewsd, &lowertemp, 0, 0);
1793 SCP(myoffset, SC_LOCAL);
1794 DTYPEP(myoffset, astb.bnd.dtype);
1795 if (STD_PAR(beforestd) || STD_TASK(beforestd)) {
1796 SCP(myoffset, SC_PRIVATE);
1797 }
1798 astoffset = mk_id(myoffset);
1799 }
1800 insert_assign(astoffset, astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
1801 /* else */
1802 newif = mk_stmt(A_ELSE, 0);
1803 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1804 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1805 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1806 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1807 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1808 /* newsd[d].lbound = 1 */
1809 insert_assign(get_global_lower(sptrnewsd, d), astb.bnd.one, beforestd);
1810 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1811 /* newsd[d].ubound = extent */
1812 insert_assign(get_global_upper(sptrnewsd, d), astextent, beforestd);
1813 }
1814 /* set myoffset = lower-stride */
1815 if (astlower == aststride) {
1816 insert_assign(astoffset, astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
1817 } else {
1818 insert_assign(astoffset,
1819 mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, aststride, astb.bnd.dtype),
1820 beforestd);
1821 }
1822 /* endif */
1823 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
1824 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1825 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1826 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1827 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1828 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1829 /* newsd[d].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride */
1830 insert_assign(get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, d),
1831 mk_binop(OP_MUL, aststride,
1832 get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1833 A_DTYPEG(aststride)),
1834 beforestd);
1835 /* lbasetemp += myoffset * oldsd[r].lstride */
1836 astlbase = mk_binop(OP_ADD, lbaseast,
1837 mk_binop(OP_MUL, astoffset,
1838 get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1839 A_DTYPEG(aststride)),
1840 A_DTYPEG(aststride));
1841 lbaseast = symvalue(astlbase, 'b', sptroldsd, &lbasetemp, 1, 0);
1842 } else {
1843 int newstride;
1844 /* newsd[d].lbound = 1 */
1845 insert_assign(get_global_lower(sptrnewsd, d), astb.bnd.one, beforestd);
1846 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1847 /* newsd[d].ubound = extent */
1848 insert_assign(get_global_upper(sptrnewsd, d), astextent, beforestd);
1849 }
1850 /* newsd[d].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride */
1851 if (r == 0 && SDSCS1G(sptroldsd)) {
1852 /* linear stride of 1st dimension here is always 1 */
1853 newstride = aststride;
1854#ifdef SDSCCONTIGG
1855 } else if (r == 0 && SDSCCONTIGG(sptroldsd)) {
1856 /* linear stride of 1st dimension here is always 1 */
1857 newstride = aststride;
1858#endif
1859 } else {
1860 newstride =
1861 mk_binop(OP_MUL, aststride, get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1862 A_DTYPEG(aststride));
1863 }
1864 insert_assign(get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, d), newstride, beforestd);
1865 if (astlower != aststride) {
1866 /* lbasetemp += (lower-stride) * oldsd[r].lstride */
1867 astlbase = mk_binop(
1868 OP_ADD, lbaseast,
1869 mk_binop(OP_MUL, get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1870 mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, aststride, astb.bnd.dtype),
1871 astb.bnd.dtype),
1872 astb.bnd.dtype);
1873 lbaseast = symvalue(astlbase, 'b', sptroldsd, &lbasetemp, 1, 0);
1874 }
1875 }
1876 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
1877 /* newsd[d].sstride = 1 */
1878 insert_assign(get_section_stride(sptrnewsd, d), astb.bnd.one,
1879 beforestd);
1880 /* newsd[d].soffset = 0 */
1881 insert_assign(get_section_offset(sptrnewsd, d), astb.bnd.zero,
1882 beforestd);
1883 }
1884 if (computesequential && flagsseq) {
1885 if (flagstemp == 0) {
1886 int sptrfunc;
1887 newsymnum++;
1888 flagstemp = getnewccsym('f', newsymnum, ST_VAR);
1889 SCP(flagstemp, SC_LOCAL);
1890 DTYPEP(flagstemp, astb.bnd.dtype);
1891 if (STD_PAR(beforestd) || STD_TASK(beforestd)) {
1892 SCP(flagstemp, SC_PRIVATE);
1893 }
1894 /* flags = oldflags */
1895 insert_assign(mk_id(flagstemp), flagsast, beforestd);
1896 flagsast = mk_id(flagstemp);
1897
1898 /* if( descriptor_length == datatype_length ) then
1899 * flags = flags | SEQUENTIAL
1900 * endif */
1901 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
1902 newargt = mk_argt(1);
1903 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = get_kind(sptrnewsd);
1904 sptrfunc = sym_mkfunc("__get_size_of", DT_INT);
1905 funcast = mk_func_node(A_FUNC, mk_id(sptrfunc), 1, newargt);
1906 cmp = mk_binop(OP_EQ, get_byte_len(sptrnewsd), funcast, DT_LOG);
1907 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1908 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1909 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1910 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1911 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1912 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1913
1914 newargt = mk_argt(2);
1915 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = flagsast;
1916 f = SEQSECTION;
1917 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = mk_isz_cval(f, dtype);
1918 funcast = mk_func_node(A_INTR, mk_id(intast_sym[I_OR]), 2, newargt);
1919 A_OPTYPEP(funcast, I_OR);
1920 A_DTYPEP(funcast, dtype);
1921 insert_assign(flagsast, funcast, beforestd);
1922
1923 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
1924 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1925 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1926 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1927 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1928 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1929 }
1930 /* if newsd[d].lstride != gsizetemp then */
1931 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
1932 cmp = mk_binop(OP_NE, get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, d), gsizeast,
1933 DT_LOG);
1934 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
1935 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1936 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1937 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1938 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1939 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1940 /* flags &= ~SEQUENTIAL_SECTION */
1941 newargt = mk_argt(2);
1942 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 0) = flagsast;
1943 f = SEQSECTION;
1944 f = ~f;
1945 ARGT_ARG(newargt, 1) = mk_isz_cval(f, dtype);
1946 funcast = mk_func_node(A_INTR, mk_id(intast_sym[I_AND]), 2, newargt);
1947 A_OPTYPEP(funcast, I_AND);
1948 A_DTYPEP(funcast, dtype);
1949 insert_assign(flagsast, funcast, beforestd);
1950 /* endif */
1951 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
1952 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
1953 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
1954 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
1955 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
1956 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
1957 }
1958 if (needgsize) {
1959 /* gsizetemp *= extent */
1960 astgsize = mk_binop(OP_MUL, gsizeast, astextent, astb.bnd.dtype);
1961 gsizeast = symvalue(astgsize, 'g', sptroldsd, &gsizetemp, 1, 0);
1962 }
1963 ++d;
1964 } else if (!(flags & SECTZBASE)) {
1965 /* single dimension */
1966 /* lbasetemp += oldsd[r].lstride * lower */
1967 astlbase = mk_binop(OP_ADD, lbaseast,
1968 mk_binop(OP_MUL, get_local_multiplier(sptroldsd, r),
1969 astlower, astb.bnd.dtype),
1970 astb.bnd.dtype);
1971 lbaseast = symvalue(astlbase, 'b', sptroldsd, &lbasetemp, 1, 0);
1972 }
1973 }
1974 /* newsd.flags = flags */
1975 insert_assign(get_desc_flags(sptrnewsd), flagsast, beforestd);
1976 /* newsd.lbase = lbasetemp */
1977 insert_assign(get_xbase(sptrnewsd), lbaseast, beforestd);
1978 if (needgsize) {
1979 /* newsd.gsize = gsizetemp */
1980 insert_assign(get_desc_gsize(sptrnewsd), gsizeast, beforestd);
1981 /* newsd.lsize = gsizetemp */
1982 insert_assign(get_desc_lsize(sptrnewsd), gsizeast, beforestd);
1983 } else {
1984 /* copy newsd.gsize = oldsd.gsize */
1985 insert_assign(get_desc_gsize(sptrnewsd), get_desc_gsize(sptroldsd),
1986 beforestd);
1987 /* copy newsd.lsize = oldsd.lsize */
1988 insert_assign(get_desc_lsize(sptrnewsd), get_desc_lsize(sptroldsd),
1989 beforestd);
1990 }
1991 /* newsd.tag = DESCRIPTOR */
1992 insert_assign(get_desc_tag(sptrnewsd), mk_isz_cval(TAGDESC, dtype),
1993 beforestd);
1994 return 1;
1995} /* _sect */
1996
1997/*
1998 * replace RTE_template[123] calls
1999 * RTE_template[123]( newsd, flags, kind, bytelen [,lower, upper] )
2000 *
2001 * newsd.rank = rank -- must be constant
2002 * newsd.kind = kind
2003 * newsd.bytelen = bytelen
2004 * newsd.gbase = 0
2005 * d=0
2006 * lbasetemp = 1
2007 * gsizetemp = 1
2008 * for r = 0 to rank-1 do
2009 * upper = upper[r]
2010 * lower = lower[r]
2011 * set extent=upper-lower+1
2012 * if upper < lower then extent = 0; upper = lower-1; endif
2013 * newsd[d].extent = extent
2014 * newsd[d].lbound = lower
2015 * newsd[d].ubound = upper
2016 * newsd[d].lstride = gsizetemp
2017 * lbasetemp -= lower * gsizetemp
2018 * newsd[d].sstride = 1
2019 * newsd[d].soffset = 0
2020 * set gsizetemp *= extent
2021 * endfor
2022 * newsd.flags = flags
2023 * newsd.lbase = lbasetemp
2024 * newsd.lsize = gsizetemp
2025 * newsd.gsize = gsizetemp
2026 * newsd.tag = DESCRIPTOR
2027 */
2028static int
2029_template(int ast, int rank, LOGICAL usevalue, int i8)
2030{
2031 int argt;
2032 int astnewsd, astflags, argbase;
2033 int sptrnewsd;
2034 int flags;
2035 int newstd, astgsize, gsizeast, lbaseast, astlbase;
2036 int gsizetemp = 0, lbasetemp = 0;
2037 int lowertemp = 0, uppertemp = 0, extenttemp = 0;
2038 int newif, cmp;
2039 int r;
2040 int dtype = DT_INT;
2041 if (i8)
2042 dtype = DT_INT8;
2043 argt = A_ARGSG(ast);
2044 astnewsd = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
2045 if (A_TYPEG(astnewsd) != A_ID)
2046 return 0;
2047 sptrnewsd = A_SPTRG(astnewsd);
2048 if (rank > 0) {
2049 /* known number of dimensions */
2050 argbase = 0;
2051 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) != 2 * rank + 4)
2052 return 0;
2053 } else {
2054 int astrank;
2055 argbase = 1;
2056 astrank = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, argbase);
2057 if (astrank <= 0)
2058 return 0;
2059 if (A_TYPEG(astrank) != A_CNST)
2060 return 0;
2061 rank = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(astrank));
2062 if (A_ARGCNTG(ast) != 2 * rank + 5)
2063 return 0;
2064 }
2065 astflags = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, argbase + 1);
2066 if (astflags <= 0)
2067 return 0;
2068 if (A_TYPEG(astflags) != A_CNST)
2069 return 0;
2070 flags = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(astflags));
2071 if (flags & 0x100) /* BOGUSFLAG */
2072 return 0;
2073 flags |= TEMPLATE | SEQSECTION;
2074
2075 /* set newsd.rank = rank */
2076 insert_assign(get_desc_rank(sptrnewsd), mk_isz_cval(rank, astb.bnd.dtype),
2077 beforestd);
2078 /* copy newsd.kind = kind */
2079 insert_assign(get_kind(sptrnewsd), VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, argbase + 2),
2080 beforestd);
2081 /* copy newsd.len = len */
2082 insert_assign(get_byte_len(sptrnewsd), VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, argbase + 3),
2083 beforestd);
2084 /* initialize lbasetemp */
2085 lbaseast = astb.bnd.one;
2086
2087 gsizeast = astb.bnd.one;
2088 for (r = 0; r < rank; ++r) {
2089 int astextent;
2090 int astlower = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, argbase + 4 + 2 * r);
2091 int astupper = VALUE_ARGT_ARG(argt, argbase + 5 + 2 * r);
2092 astlower = symvalue(astlower, 'l', sptrnewsd, &lowertemp, 0, 0);
2093 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
2094 astupper = symvalue(astupper, 'u', sptrnewsd, &uppertemp, 0, sptrnewsd);
2095 }
2096 /* section dimension */
2097 if (astlower == astb.bnd.one) {
2098 astextent = astupper;
2099 } else {
2100 astextent = mk_binop(OP_SUB, astupper, astlower, A_DTYPEG(astupper));
2101 astextent =
2102 mk_binop(OP_ADD, astextent, astb.bnd.one, A_DTYPEG(astextent));
2103 }
2104 if (A_TYPEG(astextent) == A_CNST) {
2105 ISZ_T extent = CONVAL2G(A_SPTRG(astextent));
2106 if (extent <= 0) {
2107 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
2108 astupper =
2109 mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, astb.bnd.one, A_DTYPEG(astlower));
2110 }
2111 extent = 0;
2112 astextent = astb.bnd.zero;
2113 } else {
2114 astextent = mk_isz_cval(extent, A_DTYPEG(astextent));
2115 }
2116 } else {
2117 astextent =
2118 symvalue(astextent, 'x', sptrnewsd, &extenttemp, 1, sptrnewsd);
2119 /* make sure upper bound is in a variable */
2120 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
2121 astupper = symvalue(astupper, 'u', sptrnewsd, &uppertemp, 1, sptrnewsd);
2122 }
2123 /* if(ub < lb) */
2124 newif = mk_stmt(A_IFTHEN, 0);
2125 cmp = mk_binop(OP_LT, astupper, astlower, DT_LOG);
2126 A_IFEXPRP(newif, cmp);
2127 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
2128 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
2129 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
2130 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
2131 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
2132 /* extent = 0 */
2133 insert_assign(astextent, astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
2134 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
2135 /* upper = lower-1 */
2136 insert_assign(astupper, mk_binop(OP_SUB, astlower, astb.bnd.one,
2137 A_DTYPEG(astlower)),
2138 beforestd);
2139 }
2140 /* endif */
2141 newif = mk_stmt(A_ENDIF, 0);
2142 newstd = add_stmt_before(newif, beforestd);
2143 STD_PAR(newstd) = STD_PAR(beforestd);
2144 STD_TASK(newstd) = STD_TASK(beforestd);
2145 STD_ACCEL(newstd) = STD_ACCEL(beforestd);
2146 STD_KERNEL(newstd) = STD_KERNEL(beforestd);
2147 }
2148 /* newsd[r].extent = extent */
2149 insert_assign(get_extent(sptrnewsd, r), astextent, beforestd);
2150
2151 /* newsd[r].lbound = lower */
2152 insert_assign(get_global_lower(sptrnewsd, r), astlower, beforestd);
2153 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
2154 /* newsd[r].ubound = upper */
2155 insert_assign(get_global_upper(sptrnewsd, r), astupper, beforestd);
2156 }
2157 /* newsd[r].lstride = stride * oldsd[r].lstride */
2158 insert_assign(get_local_multiplier(sptrnewsd, r), gsizeast, beforestd);
2159 if (astlower != astb.bnd.zero) {
2160 astlbase = mk_binop(OP_SUB, lbaseast,
2161 mk_binop(OP_MUL, gsizeast, astlower, astb.bnd.dtype),
2162 astb.bnd.dtype);
2163 lbaseast = symvalue(astlbase, 'b', sptrnewsd, &lbasetemp, 0, 0);
2164 }
2165 if (XBIT(70, 0x800000)) {
2166 /* newsd[r].sstride = 1 */
2167 insert_assign(get_section_stride(sptrnewsd, r), astb.bnd.one, beforestd);
2168 /* newsd[r].soffset = 0 */
2169 insert_assign(get_section_offset(sptrnewsd, r), astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
2170 }
2171 /* gsizetemp *= extent */
2172 astgsize = mk_binop(OP_MUL, gsizeast, astextent, astb.bnd.dtype);
2173 gsizeast = symvalue(astgsize, 'g', sptrnewsd, &gsizetemp, 1, 0);
2174 }
2175 /* newsd.flags = flags */
2176 insert_assign(get_desc_flags(sptrnewsd), mk_isz_cval(flags, astb.bnd.dtype),
2177 beforestd);
2178 /* newsd.lbase = lbasetemp */
2179 insert_assign(get_xbase(sptrnewsd), lbaseast, beforestd);
2180 /* newsd.gbase = 0 */
2181 insert_assign(get_gbase(sptrnewsd), astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
2182 if (XBIT(49, 0x100) && !XBIT(49, 0x80000000) && !XBIT(68, 0x1)) {
2183 /* pointers are two ints long */
2184 insert_assign(get_gbase2(sptrnewsd), astb.bnd.zero, beforestd);
2185 }
2186 /* newsd.gsize = gsizetemp */
2187 insert_assign(get_desc_gsize(sptrnewsd), gsizeast, beforestd);
2188 /* newsd.lsize = gsizetemp */
2189 insert_assign(get_desc_lsize(sptrnewsd), gsizeast, beforestd);
2190 /* newsd.tag = DESCRIPTOR */
2191 insert_assign(get_desc_tag(sptrnewsd), mk_isz_cval(TAGDESC, dtype),
2192 beforestd);
2193 return 1;
2194} /* _template */
2195
2196/*
2197 * section descriptor member
2198 */
2199static int
2200_sd_member(int subscript, int sdx, int sdtype)
2201{
2202 int subscr[2];
2203 subscr[0] = mk_isz_cval(subscript, sdtype);
2204 return mk_subscr(sdx, subscr, 1, sdtype);
2205} /* _sd_member */
2206
2207/** \brief This routine assigns a size to a descriptor's length field.
2208 *
2209 * \param ast is the expression that has the descriptor
2210 * (e.g., an A_ID, A_MEM, etc.).
2211 * \param ddesc is the symbol table pointer of the descriptor.
2212 * \param sz is the AST representing the size.
2213 *
2214 * \return the resulting assignment AST.
2215 */
2216int
2217gen_set_len_ast(int ast, SPTR ddesc, int sz)
2218{
2219
2220 DTYPE dtype;
2221 int ast2;
2222
2223 dtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
2224
2225 ast2 = mk_id(ddesc);
2226 ast2 = _sd_member(DESC_HDR_BYTE_LEN, ast2, dtype);
2227 A_DTYPEP(ast2, dtype);
2228
2229 ast2 = check_member(ast, ast2);
2230
2231 return mk_assn_stmt(ast2, sz, dtype);
2232
2233}

2236
2237LOGICAL
2238inline_RTE_set_type(int ddesc, int sdesc, int stmt, int after,
2239 DTYPE src_dtype, int astmem)
2240{
2241 /* This function inlines RTE_set_type calls. Returns TRUE if successful,
2242 * else FALSE. The src_dtype is the declared type of the source object.
2243 */
2244
2245 int stdx, asn;
2246 int subscript;
2247 int ast1, ast2;
2248 DTYPE sdtype, dtype;
2249
2250 if (is_array_dtype(src_dtype))
2251 src_dtype = array_element_dtype(src_dtype);
2252
2253 if (SCG(sdesc) == SC_DUMMY || SCG(ddesc) == SC_DUMMY) {
2254 /* TBD */
2255 return FALSE;
2256 }
2257
2258 sdtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
2259
2260 if (XBIT(49, 0x100) && !XBIT(49, 0x80000000) && !XBIT(68, 0x1)) {
2261 subscript = DESC_HDR_GBASE + 2;
2262 dtype = DT_INT8;
2263 } else {
2264 subscript = DESC_HDR_GBASE + 1;
2265 dtype = astb.bnd.dtype;
2266 }
2267
2268 ast1 = mk_id(ddesc);
2269 ast1 = _sd_member(subscript, ast1, sdtype);
2270 A_DTYPEP(ast1, dtype);
2271
2272 if (CLASSG(sdesc)) {
2273 ast2 = mk_id(sdesc);
2274 ast2 = mk_unop(OP_LOC, ast2, dtype);
2275 } else {
2276 ast2 = mk_id(sdesc);
2277 ast2 = _sd_member(subscript, ast2, sdtype);
2278 A_DTYPEP(ast2, dtype);
2279 }
2280 if (ast1 && astmem && STYPEG(ddesc) == ST_MEMBER) {
2281 ast1 = check_member(astmem, ast1);
2282 }
2283
2284 if (ast1 && ast2) {
2285 asn = mk_assn_stmt(ast1, ast2, dtype);
2286 if (SCG(ddesc) != SC_EXTERN)
2287 ADDRTKNP(ddesc, 1);
2288 if (SCG(sdesc) != SC_EXTERN)
2289 ADDRTKNP(sdesc, 1);
2290 } else {
2291 return FALSE;
2292 }
2293 if (after)
2294 stdx = add_stmt_after(asn, stmt);
2295 else
2296 stdx = add_stmt_before(asn, stmt);
2297
2298 return TRUE;
2299}

2301/*
2302 * copy one element from target section descriptor to pointer descriptor
2303 */
2304static void
2305_ptrassign_copy(int subscript, int ptrsdx, int tgtsdx, int sdtype)
2306{

2308 asn = MKASSN(_sd_member(subscript, ptrsdx, sdtype),
2309 _sd_member(subscript, tgtsdx, sdtype));
2310 stdx = add_stmt_before(asn, beforestd);
2311} /* _ptrassign_copy */
2312
2313/*
2314 * set one element in pointer section descriptor
2315 */
2316static void
2317_ptrassign_set(int subscript, int ptrsdx, int value, int sdtype)
2318{
2319 int stdx, asn;
2320 asn =
2321 MKASSN(_sd_member(subscript, ptrsdx, sdtype), mk_isz_cval(value, sdtype));
2322 stdx = add_stmt_before(asn, beforestd);

2325/*
2326 * set one element in pointer section descriptor
2327 */
2328static void
2329_ptrassign_set_ast(int subscript, int ptrsdx, int valastx, int sdtype)
2330{
2331 int stdx, asn;
2332 asn = MKASSN(_sd_member(subscript, ptrsdx, sdtype), valastx);
2333 stdx = add_stmt_before(asn, beforestd);
2334} /* _ptrassign_set_ast */
2335
2336/*
2337 * if this is a ptr_assign call that is for the whole array (sectflag == 0)
2338 * then replace by inline code.
2339 * if the pointer target is itself a pointer or allocatable,
2340 * copy the pointer value
2341 * else
2342 * replace by %loc(pointer target)
2343 * generate a loop to copy the descriptor
2344 */
2345static int
2346_ptrassign(int astx)
2347{
2348 int argt, sectflagx;
2349 int ptrx, ptrsdx, ptrsptr = 0, ptrsdsptr, ptrsdtype, tgtx, tgtsdx, tgtsptr;
2350 int asn, stdx, i, rank;
2351 argt = A_ARGSG(astx);
2352 sectflagx = ARGT_ARG(argt, 4);
2353 ptrx = ARGT_ARG(argt, 0);
2354 ptrsdx = ARGT_ARG(argt, 1);
2355 tgtx = ARGT_ARG(argt, 2);
2356 tgtsdx = ARGT_ARG(argt, 3);
2357 /* if the target is not an ID or MEMBER, give up */
2358 if (A_TYPEG(tgtx) != A_ID && A_TYPEG(tgtx) != A_MEM)
2359 return 0;
2360 /* if the target section descriptor is not an ID or MEMBER or CONST, give up
2361 */
2362 if (A_TYPEG(tgtsdx) != A_ID && A_TYPEG(tgtsdx) != A_MEM &&
2363 A_TYPEG(tgtsdx) != A_CNST)
2364 return 0;
2365 /* if the destination pointer is not an ID or MEMBER, give up */
2366 if (A_TYPEG(ptrx) != A_ID && A_TYPEG(ptrx) != A_MEM)
2367 return 0;
2368 /* if the destination section descriptor is not an ID or MEMBER, give up */
2369 if (A_TYPEG(ptrsdx) != A_ID && A_TYPEG(ptrsdx) != A_MEM)
2370 return 0;
2371 if (sectflagx != astb.i0 && sectflagx != astb.k0 &&
2372 (tgtsdx != ptrsdx /*|| XBIT(1,0x800)*/))
2373 /* leave the call in place */
2374 return 0;
2375 /* if the target is itself a pointer, we can simply copy the pointer value */
2376 if (A_TYPEG(tgtx) == A_ID) {
2377 tgtsptr = A_SPTRG(tgtx);
2378 } else if (A_TYPEG(tgtx) == A_MEM) {
2379 tgtsptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(tgtx));
2380 }
2381 if (A_TYPEG(ptrx) == A_ID) {
2382 ptrsptr = A_SPTRG(ptrx);
2383 } else if (A_TYPEG(ptrx) == A_MEM) {
2384 ptrsptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(ptrx));
2385 }
2386#ifdef TEXTUREG
2387 if (ptrsptr && TEXTUREG(ptrsptr))
2388 return 0;
2389#endif
2390#ifdef DEVICEG
2391 if (ptrsptr && DEVICEG(ptrsptr))
2392 return 0;
2393#endif
2394 if (A_TYPEG(ptrsdx) == A_ID) {
2395 ptrsdsptr = A_SPTRG(ptrsdx);
2396 if (STYPEG(ptrsptr) == ST_MEMBER && STYPEG(ptrsdsptr) != ST_MEMBER) {
2397 ptrsdsptr = 0;
2398 }
2399 } else if (A_TYPEG(ptrsdx) == A_MEM) {
2400 ptrsdsptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(ptrsdx));
2401 }
2402 if (MIDNUMG(ptrsptr) == 0)
2403 return 0;
2404 if (POINTERG(tgtsptr)) {
2405 if (MIDNUMG(tgtsptr) == 0)
2406 return 0;
2407 /* copy the pointer */
2408 asn = MKASSN(check_member(ptrx, mk_id(MIDNUMG(ptrsptr))),
2409 check_member(tgtx, mk_id(MIDNUMG(tgtsptr))));
2410 } else {
2411 /* must take %loc(arg) */
2412 asn = MKASSN(check_member(ptrx, mk_id(MIDNUMG(ptrsptr))),
2413 mk_unop(OP_LOC, tgtx, DT_PTR));
2414 }
2415 stdx = add_stmt_before(asn, beforestd);
2416 if (ptrsdsptr) {
2417 ptrsdtype = DDTG(DTYPEG(ptrsdsptr));
2418 if (A_TYPEG(tgtsdx) == A_ID) {
2419 tgtsdx = mk_id(A_SPTRG(tgtsdx));
2420 } else if (A_TYPEG(tgtsdx) == A_MEM) {
2421 tgtsdx = mk_member(A_PARENTG(tgtsdx), mk_id(A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(tgtsdx))),
2422 A_DTYPEG(tgtsdx));
2423 }
2424 if (A_TYPEG(tgtsdx) == A_CNST) {
2425 /* PTRSD(tag) = value */
2426 _ptrassign_set_ast(DESC_HDR_TAG, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2427 } else if (ptrsdx != tgtsdx) {
2428 /* PTRSD(tag) = Descriptor */
2429 /* PTRSD(rank) = TGTSD(rank) */
2430 /* PTRSD(kind) = TGTSD(kind) */
2431 /* PTRSD(len) = TGTSD(len) */
2432 /* PTRSD(flags) = TGTSD(flags) */
2433 /* PTRSD(lsize) = TGTSD(lsize) */
2434 /* PTRSD(gsize) = TGTSD(gsize) */
2435 /* PTRSD(lbase) = TGTSD(lbase) */
2436 /* PTRSD(gbase) = TGTSD(gbase) */
2437 /* for i = 0; i < rank ++i */
2438 /* PTRSD(lower(i)) = 1 */
2439 /* PTRSD(extent(i)) = TGTSD(extent(i)) */
2440 /* PTRSD(upper(i)) = TGTSD(extent(i)) */
2441 /* PTRSD(lstride(i)) = TGTSD(lstride(i)) */
2442 /* PTRSD(soffset(i)) = 0 */
2443 /* PTRSD(sstride(i)) = 0 */
2444 _ptrassign_set(DESC_HDR_TAG, ptrsdx, TAGDESC, ptrsdtype);
2445 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_RANK, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2446 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_KIND, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2447 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_BYTE_LEN, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2448 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_FLAGS, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2449 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_LSIZE, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2450 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_GSIZE, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2451 if (ASSUMSHPG(tgtsptr) && !XBIT(58, 0x400000)) {
2452 _ptrassign_set(DESC_HDR_LBASE, ptrsdx, 1, ptrsdtype);
2453 } else {
2454 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_LBASE, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2455 }
2456 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_GBASE, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2457 if (XBIT(49, 0x100) && !XBIT(49, 0x80000000)
2458 && !XBIT(68, 0x1)
2459 ) {
2460 /* pointers are two ints long */
2461 _ptrassign_copy(DESC_HDR_GBASE + 1, ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2462 }
2463 rank = ADD_NUMDIM(DTYPEG(ptrsptr));
2464 for (i = 0; i < rank; ++i) {
2465 int lb;
2466 if (!ASSUMSHPG(tgtsptr) || XBIT(58, 0x400000)) {
2467 _ptrassign_copy(get_global_lower_index(i), ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2468 } else {
2469 /* for assumed-shape arguments, use the declared bounds */
2470 lb = ADD_LWAST(DTYPEG(tgtsptr), i);
2471 _ptrassign_set_ast(get_global_lower_index(i), ptrsdx, lb, ptrsdtype);
2472 }
2473 _ptrassign_copy(get_global_extent_index(i), ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2474 _ptrassign_set(get_section_stride_index(i), ptrsdx, 0, ptrsdtype);
2475 _ptrassign_set(get_section_offset_index(i), ptrsdx, 0, ptrsdtype);
2476 _ptrassign_copy(get_multiplier_index(i), ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype);
2477 if (ASSUMSHPG(tgtsptr) && !XBIT(58, 0x400000)) {
2478 /* adjust the LBASE */
2479 int a;
2480 a = mk_binop(OP_MUL,
2481 _sd_member(get_multiplier_index(i), ptrsdx, ptrsdtype),
2482 lb, ptrsdtype);
2483 a = mk_binop(OP_SUB, _sd_member(DESC_HDR_LBASE, ptrsdx, ptrsdtype), a,
2484 ptrsdtype);
2485 _ptrassign_set_ast(DESC_HDR_LBASE, ptrsdx, a, ptrsdtype);
2486 }
2487 /* we could copy the upper bound, but it's never used by the runtime
2488 * anyway */
2489 /* _ptrassign_copy( get_global_upper_index(i), ptrsdx, tgtsdx, ptrsdtype
2490 * );*/
2491 }
2492 }
2493 }
2494 return 1; /* ### */
2495} /* _ptrassign */
2496
2497/*
2498 * inline RTE_sect calls, where possible
2499 * also inline simple ptr2_assign calls, where the pointee is the whole array
2500 * do this after sectfloat
2501 */
2502void
2503sectinline(void)
2504{
2505 int std, stdnext;
2506 int ast;
2507
2508 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = stdnext) {
2509 stdnext = STD_NEXT(std);
2510 ast = STD_AST(std);
2511 beforestd = std;
2512 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CALL) {
2513 int lop;
2514 lop = A_LOPG(ast);
2515 if (lop && A_TYPEG(lop) == A_ID) {
2516 int fsptr;
2517 fsptr = A_SPTRG(lop);
2518 if (HCCSYMG(fsptr) && STYPEG(fsptr) == ST_PROC) {
2519 int i;
2520 i = getF90TmplSectRtn(SYMNAME(fsptr));
2521 switch (i & FTYPE_MASK) {
2522 case FTYPE_SECT:
2523 /* found one of the names */
2524 if (_sect(ast, i & FTYPE_I8)) {
2525 ast_to_comment(ast);
2526 }
2527 break;
2528 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE:
2529 if (_template(ast, -1, FALSE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2530 ast_to_comment(ast);
2531 break;
2532 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE1:
2533 if (_template(ast, 1, FALSE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2534 ast_to_comment(ast);
2535 break;
2536 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE1V:
2537 if (_template(ast, 1, TRUE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2538 ast_to_comment(ast);
2539 break;
2540 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE2:
2541 if (_template(ast, 2, FALSE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2542 ast_to_comment(ast);
2543 break;
2544 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE2V:
2545 if (_template(ast, 2, TRUE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2546 ast_to_comment(ast);
2547 break;
2548 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE3:
2549 if (_template(ast, 3, FALSE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2550 ast_to_comment(ast);
2551 break;
2552 case FTYPE_TEMPLATE3V:
2553 if (_template(ast, 3, TRUE, i & FTYPE_I8))
2554 ast_to_comment(ast);
2555 break;
2556 }
2557 }
2558 }
2559 } else if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ICALL) {
2560 switch (A_OPTYPEG(ast)) {
2561 case I_PTR2_ASSIGN:
2562 /* see if this can be inlined */
2563 if (_ptrassign(ast)) {
2564 ast_to_comment(ast);
2565 }
2566 break;
2567 }
2568 }
2569 }
2570} /* sectinline */
2571
2572static void
2573convert_statements(void)
2574{
2575 int std, stdnext;
2576 int ast;
2577 int parallel_depth;
2578 int task_depth;
2579
2580 init_tbl();
2581 unvisit_every_sptr();
2582
2583 parallel_depth = 0;
2584 task_depth = 0;
2585 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = stdnext) {
2586 stdnext = STD_NEXT(std);
2587 ast = STD_AST(std);
2588 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
2589 case A_ALLOC:
2590 if (A_TKNG(ast) == TK_ALLOCATE) {
2591 stdnext = conv_allocate(std);
2592 } else {
2593 assert(A_TKNG(ast) == TK_DEALLOCATE, "conv_statements: bad dealloc",
2594 std, 4);
2595 stdnext = conv_deallocate(std);
2596 }
2597 break;
2598 case A_MP_PARALLEL:
2599 ++parallel_depth;
2600 /*symutl.sc = SC_PRIVATE;*/
2601 set_descriptor_sc(SC_PRIVATE);
2602 break;
2603 case A_MP_ENDPARALLEL:
2604 --parallel_depth;
2605 if (parallel_depth == 0 && task_depth == 0) {
2606 /*symutl.sc = SC_LOCAL;*/
2607 set_descriptor_sc(SC_LOCAL);
2608 }
2609 break;
2610 case A_MP_TASK:
2611 case A_MP_TASKLOOP:
2612 ++task_depth;
2613 set_descriptor_sc(SC_PRIVATE);
2614 break;
2615 case A_MP_ENDTASK:
2616 case A_MP_ETASKLOOP:
2617 --task_depth;
2618 if (parallel_depth == 0 && task_depth == 0) {
2619 set_descriptor_sc(SC_LOCAL);
2620 }
2621 break;
2622 default:
2623 break;
2624 }
2625 }
2626 free_tbl();
2627}
2628
2629static void
2630_mark_descr(int ast, int *dummy)
2631{
2632 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_MEM)
2633 ast = A_MEMG(ast);
2634 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ID) {
2635 int sptr, stype;
2636 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
2637 stype = STYPEG(sptr);
2638 if ((stype == ST_ARRAY || stype == ST_MEMBER) && DESCARRAYG(sptr)) {
2639 VISITP(sptr, 1);
2640 }
2641 }
2642} /* _mark_descr */
2643
2644static void
2645convert_template_instance(void)
2646{
2647 int sptr, std, stdnext;
2648 /* we are looking for cases where we have a RTE_template call
2649 * followed by a pghpf_instance call, and the pghpf_instance call
2650 * is the ONLY use of the RTE_template output template.
2651 * for instance
2652 * call RTE_template(aa$sd,1,2,0,0,1,20)
2653 * call pghpf_instance(aa$sd1,aa$sd,27,4,0)
2654 * replace aa$sd by aa$sd1 here
2655 */
2656
2657 /* reset VISIT flags */
2658 for (sptr = stb.firstosym; sptr < stb.stg_avail; ++sptr) {
2659 VISITP(sptr, 0);
2660 }
2661
2662 /* Look for all uses of section descriptors anywhere
2663 * outside of calls to RTE_template and pghpf_instance */
2664 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = stdnext) {
2665 int ast, sptr, argcnt, dummy;
2666 stdnext = STD_NEXT(std);
2667 ast = STD_AST(std);
2668 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
2669 case A_CALL:
2670 sptr = memsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(ast));
2671 if (STYPEG(sptr) != ST_PROC)
2672 break;
2673 argcnt = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
2674 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_PROC) {
2675 /* don't look at RTE_template calls */
2676 if (strcmp(SYMNAME(sptr), mkRteRtnNm(RTE_template)) == 0)
2677 break;
2678 /* don't look at pghpf_instance calls
2679 * if the previous statement is a RTE_template call */
2680 if (strcmp(SYMNAME(sptr), mkRteRtnNm(RTE_instance)) == 0) {
2681 int stdprev, astprev;
2682 stdprev = STD_PREV(std);
2683 astprev = STD_AST(stdprev);
2684 if (A_TYPEG(astprev) == A_CALL) {
2685 int sptrprev;
2686 sptrprev = A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(astprev));
2687 if (STYPEG(sptrprev) == ST_PROC &&
2688 strcmp(SYMNAME(sptrprev), mkRteRtnNm(RTE_template)) == 0)
2689 break;
2690 }
2691 }
2692 }
2693 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
2694 default:
2695 ast_visit(1, 1);
2696 ast_traverse(ast, NULL, _mark_descr, &dummy);
2697 ast_unvisit();
2698 break;
2699 }
2700 }
2701 /* Look for pghpf_instance calls where the previous statement
2702 * is a RTE_template call, or the previous two statements are
2703 * a RTE_set_intrin_type call and a RTE_template call, and where
2704 * the input descriptor to the instance is the output descriptor of the
2705 * template call, and the descriptor has no other uses */
2706 for (std = STD_NEXT(0); std; std = stdnext) {
2707 int ast, sptr, argcnt;
2708 stdnext = STD_NEXT(std);
2709 ast = STD_AST(std);
2710 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_CALL) {
2711 sptr = memsym_of_ast(A_LOPG(ast));
2712 argcnt = A_ARGCNTG(ast);
